source.name: Geochemistry of Soils from the Rock Analysis Storage System (RASS) Database
source.description: Geochemical data for soils collected by USGS personnel and analyzed by USGS. These data were part of the Rock Analysis Storage System and are now merged into the National Geochemistry Database.
